    "Support vector machine (SVM)The Support Vector Machine (SVM) is a supervised machine learning algorithm with various applications [125].",
    "It tries to find a decision boundary between different classes in the input feature space.",
    "The SVM must be trained at least once for recognition and class using one of many methods.",
